(71, 1, '2018-07-03 11:32:39', '2018-07-03 08:32:39', '<img class="aligncenter wp-image-33 size-full" src="http://localhost/desc/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/president-1.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="494" />\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">"Astana is a symbol of renewal of Kazakhstan, a symbol of inexhaustible creative energy of its multinational people. It is a symbol of faith people in their own force, who arrived in not good times to construct new capital. It is a symbol of hope and confidence of the nation, which gained freedom in its prosperous future, in future of their descendants". </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">President of Republic Kazakhstan Nursultan </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Abishuly</span><b> </b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Nazarbayev </span>', 'Main [en]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-07-03 11:32:39', '2018-07-03 08:32:39', '', 32, 'http://localhost/desc/2018/07/03/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
