(262, 1, '2018-07-03 23:29:28', '2018-07-03 20:29:28', '[rev_slider alias="slider1"]\r\n\r\n[rev_slider alias="slider2"]\r\n\r\nThis is a Multifunctional, scientific-analytical, and humanitarian-enlightenment governmental institution.\r\n\r\nBy the Order of the President of the Republic of Kazakhstan on 23<sup>rd</sup> January, 2012, on the basis of “Presidential cultural center” of the Republic of Kazakhstan, Multifunctional, scientific-analytical, and humanitarian-enlightenment Nazarbaev Center was built to thoroughly research and popularize the history of our country.\r\n\r\nThe aim at building Nazarbaev Center is to build information space and develop it on the basis of researching and popularizing Kazakhstan history.\r\n\r\nThe purpose of the governmental institution is to organize and conduct a systematic research of the state history, integrate in developing in humanitarian-cultural, social-economic and social-political terms. To aid the consolidation of civic equality and patriotism in the society, to ensure the cooperation and interactions between the governmental, scientific and cultural organizations and civil society institutions, the media as so to solve the problem of researching Kazakhstan history, its theory and practice and popularization.\r\n\r\nTo reach the specified goals, governmental institution is to accomplish its duty in four directions including analytical, humanitarian-enlightenment and education, bibliographic and information service, and museum service.\r\n\r\nIn addition, to help to enhance international cooperation in political, social, humanitarian and other spheres of the Republic of Kazakhstan, propagandizing its role in the international community is also one of the priorities.', 'Nazarbaev Center (2013)', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nazarbaev-center-2013__trashed', '', '', '2018-07-03 23:56:06', '2018-07-03 20:56:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/desc/?page_id=262', 0, 'page', '', 0),
