(295, 1, '2018-07-04 00:10:54', '2018-07-03 21:10:54', '[rev_slider alias="slider1"]\r\n\r\n[rev_slider alias="slider2"]\r\n\r\nThe Museum of the First President of the Republic of Kazakhstan is a museum situated in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astana">Astana</a>. It was established by Decree of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_leaders_of_Kazakhstan">President of the Republic of Kazakhstan</a>on August 28, 2004.\r\n<h2>The history of the Museum</h2>\r\nSI «Museum of the First President of the Republic of Kazakhstan» was reorganized through accession of SI «Library of the First President of the Republic of Kazakhstan – Leader of the Nation» by the Decree of the President of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kazakhstan">Republic of Kazakhstan</a> On November 4, 2016. The status of one of the leading divisions of the Library of the First President Museum received from that time.\r\n\r\nMuseum of Library of the First President of the Republic of Kazakhstan – Leader of the Nation – it’s a museum of modern history of Kazakhstan. The establishment of the state sovereignty of the Republic and historical role of its First President <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nursultan_Nazarbayev">N.A. Nazarbayev</a> in building an independent democratic state – the basic idea of its expositions.\r\n\r\nIn the Museum of Library of the First President of the Republic of Kazakhstan – Leader of the Nation for all categories of visitors are held survey and thematic excursions in Kazakh, Russian and English languages.\r\n\r\nNowadays the collection of the Museum of Library totals 37,733 units of storage, including the library fund of the museum - 2,240 books and printing editions, electronic archival fund – 25,813 units of storage, museum collection – 9 680 units of storage.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Museum of the First President of the Republic of Kazakhstan', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'museum-of-the-first-president-of-the-republic-of-kazakhstan', '', '', '2018-07-04 00:10:54', '2018-07-03 21:10:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost/desc/?p=295', 0, 'post', '', 0);
