(418, 1, '2018-07-04 02:24:00', '2018-07-03 23:24:00', '[rev_slider alias="slider1"]\r\n\r\n[rev_slider alias="slider2"]\r\n\r\nChief architect is Renato Archetti. In regards to architectural excellence, the theatre is not inferior to the famous opera theatres of the world, such as "La Rock" in Milan, the Royal Theatre in Madrid, the Metropolitan Opera in New York. The theater was built with the best classical traditions of the world architecture, the architecture emphasized Kazakh national character. A team of architects, builders and specialists of 33 countries has worked on external appearance and interior of the theater.  The stage of "Astana Opera" theatre is decorated with masterpieces of Opera and ballet classics, contemporary performances by world-class artists.', 'The state theatre of Opera and ballet "Astana Opera" (2013)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-state-theatre-of-opera-and-ballet-astana-opera-2013', '', '', '2018-07-04 02:24:00', '2018-07-03 23:24:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/desc/?p=418', 0, 'post', '', 0);
