(424, 1, '2018-07-04 02:27:43', '2018-07-03 23:27:43', '[rev_slider alias="slider1"]\r\n\r\n[rev_slider alias="slider2"]\r\n\r\nThe theatre was founded in 2012. At the initiative of President Nursultan Nazarbayev. The construction was completed in November 2016. About 1200 local builders and professionals had worked on the construction of theatre, designed by architects Corporation "Basis-A".\r\n\r\nThe architectural ensemble is harmoniously found side by side with classic and elements in the style of hi-tech, which gives the building elegance and modernity.\r\n\r\nThe total area of the theatre is 15.467 m<sup>2</sup> . The auditorium has a capacity for 783 places. The area of a scene – 536 m<sup>2</sup>. Stage complex (scene, proscenium, backstage, pockets) is more than 1000 m<sup>2</sup>. The orchestra pit is designed for 50-60 musicians. The latest technology of mobile and lifting and lowering mechanics are used for the transformation scene. The stage is equipped with 4 lifting and 4 tablets artistic lifts.\r\n\r\nThe theater has 2 rehearsal rooms, their area corresponds to the area of the scene, which is very convenient in the process of creating new plays. Both halls are equipped with sound equipment, a video recording of the rehearsals. Each of them has a piano.\r\n\r\nThe parameters and capabilities of the stage allow for the wide range of cultural activities and creative meetings, concerts, Symphony, pop and folk orchestras, to present musicals, modern show using different special effects.\r\n\r\nThe facade is made of travertine with decorative elements, stylized national patterns. The beautiful natural stone Colonnade of white color, giving the building a lightness, is located around the perimeter of the theatre.\r\n\r\nNew theatre organically fit into the architectural complex of Astana, its modern appearance blends in well with buildings of EXPO-2017.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The theater "ASTANA BALLET" (2016)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-theater-astana-ballet-2016', '', '', '2018-07-04 02:27:43', '2018-07-03 23:27:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/desc/?p=424', 0, 'post', '', 0),
